@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

### Listar todas as vendas
GET {{baseUrl}}/sales

### Buscar venda por ID (substitua o ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sales/7cfc078d-c8ea-49e9-9ad3-4ffb4f5dc302

### Criar venda (substitua userId e productId por IDs reais)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "USER_ID_AQUI",
  "items": [
    { "productId": "PRODUCT_ID_AQUI", "quantity": 2 },
    { "productId": "OUTRO_PRODUCT_ID", "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

### Cancelar venda (substitua o ID)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/sales/7cfc078d-c8ea-49e9-9ad3-4ffb4f5dc302/cancel

### --- Casos de erro ---

### Tentar criar venda sem itens (deve retornar 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "USER_ID_AQUI",
  "items": []
}

### Tentar criar venda com estoque insuficiente (deve retornar 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "USER_ID_AQUI",
  "items": [
    { "productId": "PRODUCT_ID_AQUI", "quantity": 99999 }
  ]
}

### Tentar cancelar venda já cancelada (deve retornar 409)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/sales/7cfc078d-c8ea-49e9-9ad3-4ffb4f5dc302/cancel

### Buscar venda inexistente (deve retornar 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sales/id-que-nao-existe
